    dc:creator "Dinn, Curtis; Leys, Sally P.; Roussel, Mylène; Méthé, Denise" ;
    dc:date "2020" ;
    dc:title "Geographic range extensions of stalked, flabelliform sponges (Porifera) from eastern Canada with a new combination of a species of Plicatellopsis in the North Atlantic" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3733617>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3733629>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3733631> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3733617>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Map of the collection sites in Baffin Bay/ Davis Strait (inset) and collections in the Gulf of St. Lawrence. Hollow diamonds, Axinella arctica; filled circles, Cladocroce spatula; filled squares, Semisuberites cribrosa; filled triangles, Plicatellopsis bowerbanki comb. nov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3733617/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3733629>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Plicatellopsis bowerbanki (Vosmaer, 1885) comb. nov. from eastern Canada. A. specimen in situ; B. specimens growing on rock wall in Northern Gulf of St. Lawrence; C. IML 11900 showing secondary vase extending from single base; D. specimen living amongst Keratoisis sp. coral on the western Greenland Shelf; E. CMNI 2018-0136, growing on dead Keratoisis sp. coral fragment. F. CMNI 2018-0202 from Pond Inlet, Baffin Island. In situ photo credit: DFO/CSSF/Oceana Canada (A,B); DFO/CSSF/ArcticNet (D)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3733629/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3733631>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Plicatellopsis bowerbanki (Vosmaer, 1885) comb. nov. spicules and skeleton. A. spicules; B. detail of slight tyle; C,D. SEM of tylostyle I; E,F. SEM of tylostyle II; G. skeleton of Baffin Bay specimen, ectosomal skeleton of spicule brushes are visible at the surface; H. skeleton of BMNH 1910.1.1.1477 (from lectotype)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3733631/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

